---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Sobre Nós | Zarix">
  <main class="bg-[#0B0F19] text-slate-100 min-h-screen pt-32 pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative overflow-hidden selection:bg-blue-500/30">
    
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#1e293b12_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#1e293b12_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:4rem_4rem] [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_60%_50%_at_50%_30%,#000_60%,transparent_100%)] pointer-events-none"></div>
    
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto relative z-10 space-y-28">
      
      <section class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 border-b border-slate-800 pb-16 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-xs font-mono text-blue-400 tracking-widest uppercase">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500 animate-pulse"></span>
            <span>System_Initialization // Core</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight text-white font-sans leading-none">
            Moldamos engenharia digital para <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r via-blue-400 from-blue-500 to-indigo-400">qualquer modelo de negócio.</span>
          </h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-6 lg:pl-8 lg:border-l border-slate-800/60 font-mono text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Na <span class="text-white font-bold">Zarix</span>, não acreditamos em soluções pré-fabricadas ou em templates universais que limitam a sua marca. Cada empresa opera sob regras únicas, e a sua infraestrutura digital deve refletir exatamente essa lógica.
          </p>
          <p>
            Desenvolvemos ecossistemas web sob medida, adaptando-nos cirurgicamente às reais necessidades do seu setor técnico ou comercial — desde plataformas locais de alta conversão até sistemas robustos de gestão corporativa.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>


      <section class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center border-b border-slate-800 pb-4 gap-2">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">// Matriz_Tecnologica_Global</div>
          <div class="text-xs font-mono text-blue-400/80">Modos de compilação: Nativo, Híbrido & SSR</div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 border border-slate-800 bg-[#0F1626]/20 rounded-xl divide-y lg:divide-y-0 lg:divide-x divide-slate-800 overflow-hidden">
          
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 p-8 space-y-6 bg-[#0B0F19]/40">
            <div class="space-y-1">
              <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-indigo-400 bg-indigo-500/5 border border-indigo-500/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase">Layer 01 // Back-end & Core Systems</span>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Arquitetura de Sistemas Robustos</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">Desenvolvimento de lógica complexa, algoritmos eficientes e processamento nativo que sustenta grandes volumes de dados sem latência.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="space-y-3 font-mono text-xs">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 border border-slate-800/60 bg-[#0F1626]/40 rounded hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-all group">
                <span class="text-slate-200 font-bold group-hover:text-indigo-400 transition-colors">C++ Engine Development</span>
                <span class="text-slate-500 text-[10px]">HIGH_PERFORMANCE</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 border border-slate-800/60 bg-[#0F1626]/40 rounded hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-all group">
                <span class="text-slate-200 font-bold group-hover:text-indigo-400 transition-colors">Java Enterprise Solutions</span>
                <span class="text-slate-500 text-[10px]">SCALABLE_BACKEND</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="lg:col-span-7 p-8 space-y-6">
            <div class="space-y-1">
              <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-500/5 border border-cyan-500/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase">Layer 02 // Front-end & User Interface</span>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Interfaces Adaptativas de Alta Performance</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">Desenho e implementação de layouts estéticos, fluidos e otimizados para motores de busca (SEO) com o máximo rendimento de carregamento.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 font-mono text-xs">
              <div class="p-3 border border-slate-800/80 bg-[#0B0F19]/60 rounded hover:border-blue-500/40 hover:text-white transition-all">
                <div class="text-slate-400 font-bold">Astro</div>
                <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-600 mt-1">Islands Architecture / SSR</div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-3 border border-slate-800/80 bg-[#0B0F19]/60 rounded hover:border-blue-500/40 hover:text-white transition-all">
                <div class="text-slate-400 font-bold">React</div>
                <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-600 mt-1">Dynamic Reactive UI</div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-3 border border-slate-800/80 bg-[#0B0F19]/60 rounded hover:border-blue-500/40 hover:text-white transition-all">
                <div class="text-slate-400 font-bold">Tailwind CSS</div>
                <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-600 mt-1">Utility-First Framework</div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-3 border border-slate-800/80 bg-[#0B0F19]/60 rounded hover:border-blue-500/40 hover:text-white transition-all">
                <div class="text-slate-400 font-bold">Bootstrap</div>
                <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-600 mt-1">Enterprise Layouts</div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-3 border border-slate-800/80 bg-[#0B0F19]/60 rounded hover:border-blue-500/40 hover:text-white transition-all">
                <div class="text-slate-400 font-bold">HTML5 / CSS3</div>
                <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-600 mt-1">Semantic Standard Web</div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-3 border border-slate-800/40 bg-blue-500/5 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-center border-dashed border-blue-500/20 text-blue-400/80">
                <span>& Full Stack Custom</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>


      <section class="space-y-8">
        <div class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">// Adaptabilidade_E_Escopo</div>
        
        <div class="border border-slate-800 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0F1626]/40 to-transparent p-6 md:p-10 rounded-xl space-y-8 relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute -right-16 -top-16 w-44 h-44 bg-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
          
          <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight font-sans">O Seu Setor Comercial Dita As Regras</h2>
            <p class="font-mono text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Não importa se gere um restaurante que necessita de ecrãs interativos rápidos, uma clínica médica que procura agendamentos seguros, ou uma infraestrutura industrial que exige dashboards de monitorização em tempo real. Nós analisamos os seus requisitos técnicos e construímos exatamente o que precisa para operar e vender mais.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 font-mono text-xs border-t border-slate-800/60 pt-6">
            <div class="space-y-1">
              <div class="text-white font-bold flex items-center space-x-2">
                <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
                <span>Flexibilidade de Design</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-[11px]">A interface adapta-se perfeitamente à identidade corporativa ou urbana da sua marca.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-1">
              <div class="text-white font-bold flex items-center space-x-2">
                <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
                <span>Escalabilidade Nativa</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-[11px]">O código é modular. Pode começar com uma Landing Page e expandi-la para um ERP complexo.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-1">
              <div class="text-white font-bold flex items-center space-x-2">
                <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
                <span>Otimização Absoluta</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-[11px]">Garantimos tempos mínimos de resposta de servidor e máxima pontuação em Core Web Vitals.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>


      <section class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-stretch">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-4">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">// Localização_Física</div>
          <div class="bg-[#0F1626]/30 border border-slate-800/80 rounded-xl p-6 space-y-4 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute -right-12 -top-12 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="space-y-2 relative z-10">
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-blue-400 tracking-widest uppercase">Sede_Operacional</span>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white tracking-tight font-sans">Aveiro, Portugal</h3>
              <p class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                Zarix — Suporte IT para Empresas<br/>
                <span class="text-slate-500">(Endereço completo disponível mediante agendamento)</span>
              </p>
            </div>
            <a
              href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Zarix+%E2%80%94+Suporte+IT+para+Empresas/@40.6393786,-8.6652275,14z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0xdfeef0b38947d7:0xf48f0e3e3843810!8m2!3d40.6393804!4d-8.644628!16s%2Fg%2F11nk8z317g"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[11px] text-slate-400 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors border border-slate-800/60 bg-[#0B0F19]/60 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg relative z-10"
            >
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
              <span>Ver no Google Maps</span>
              <span class="text-slate-600">↗</span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#0F1626]/30 border border-slate-800/80 rounded-xl p-6 space-y-3 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute -right-12 -top-12 w-32 h-32 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
            <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-emerald-400 tracking-widest uppercase relative z-10">Horário_Funcionamento</span>
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-400 space-y-1 relative z-10">
              <div class="flex justify-between"><span>Segunda a Sexta</span><span class="text-slate-300">09:00 — 18:00</span></div>
              <div class="flex justify-between"><span>Sábado</span><span class="text-slate-600">Fechado</span></div>
              <div class="flex justify-between"><span>Domingo</span><span class="text-slate-600">Fechado</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-7 bg-[#0F1626]/20 border border-slate-800/80 rounded-xl overflow-hidden relative min-h-[280px] flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#1e293b08_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#1e293b08_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:3rem_3rem] pointer-events-none"></div>
          <iframe
            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d24310.91108705615!2d-8.6652275!3d40.6393786!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0xdfeef0b38947d7%3A0xf48f0e3e3843810!2sZarix%20%E2%80%94%20Suporte%20IT%20para%20Empresas!5e0!3m2!1spt-PT!2spt!4v1"
            width="100%"
            height="100%"
            style="min-height: 280px; border: 0;"
            allowfullscreen=""
            loading="lazy"
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
            class="relative z-10 grayscale invert-[0.85] hue-rotate-[200deg] opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
            title="Mapa — Zarix Aveiro"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </section>

      <hr class="border-slate-800/60" />

      <section class="pt-4 text-center space-y-6">
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-slate-400">Pronto para desenhar a sua nova infraestrutura?</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4">
          <a href="/servicos" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white font-mono text-xs font-bold rounded tracking-wider uppercase transition-all duration-200 text-center shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/10">
            Ver Serviços & Pacotes
          </a>
          
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/zarix_it/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group flex items-center space-x-2 font-mono text-xs text-slate-500 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
            <span>Canal de atualizações técnicas</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
